Guanxi::Beans
=============

o Introduction
o Building
o More information
o License

Introduction
------------
The Guanxi Beans module provides an XML abstraction layer for
reading configuration information for the other Guanxi modules
as well as parsing and creating SAML messages.

Building
--------
git clone http://github.com/guanxi/guanxi-beans.git
cd guanxi-beans
mvn clean install

More information
----------------
The Guanxi blog: http://codebrane.com/blog/?cat=2

